title: Everything Wash Park Has to Offer!!
posting_body: ['Looking to get just blocks from Wash Park?', 'Wash Park Station is here to impress!', 'With light rail access a moments’ walk, getting around your favorite city will be a breeze.', 'Enjoy Denver’s 300 days of sun with floor to ceiling windows and a quick walk to everyone’s favorite sushi joint: Sushi Den.', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', '<URL> Community Amenities Non-Smoking Community • FORTE Fitness Discount • Branch Home Office Furniture Discount • 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance • Bike Storage • Smoke-Free Community • Elevator • Mountain Views • Online Rent Payments • Pet Friendly • Reserved Parking •', 'Secured Building • Walking Distance To Light Rail •', 'Move', 'In Guarantee Apartment Amenities Air Conditioner • Balcony • Designer Finishes • Dishwasher •', 'Downtown Views • Dryer • Interior Garage', 'Doors • Refrigerator • Washer • Hardwood Floors', 'LEASING CENTER HOURS', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM  Saturday: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Pets - allowed Restrictions: Exotic pets such as birds, reptiles, etc. are approved on a case-by-case basis.', 'Fish tanks weighing more than 20 pounds require additional approval.', 'Cats - 2 allowed, One time Fee $250.00, Rent $30.00 Comments: Maximum of two pets per apartment.', 'Pet weight may not exceed 80 pounds when combined.', 'Pet deposit is $250.00 and there is a pet rent of $30 a month per pet.', 'Dogs - 2 allowed, Max weight 80 lb each, One time Fee $250.00, Rent $30.00 Comments: Maximum of two pets per apartment.', 'Pet weight may not exceed 80 pounds when combined.', 'Pet deposit is $250.00 and there is a pet rent of $30 a month per pet.', 'Restrictions: Pit Bull, Doberman Pinscher, Bull Mastiff, Cane Corso, Rottweiler, or any mix thereof.']
